message.body: I gotta run out now. Can you leave the van at my house or do you need it again tomorrow.
I don't need it tomorrow but I gotta unload tonight
Ok. I mainly need the paint roller extension or the broom.
Ok. Can I drop off the van in the morning?
Yeah if leave me that stuff. I want to paint tonight.

Dropped the van off. I'm borrowing the sawzall . I'm gonna order one. Can you take the company screws out of my screw box and the nails from my nail box at some point. Btw they have those keter boxes like my nail box at Walmart now
Are you still down to work at versek's tomorrow and Friday?
Cool. We're gonna start at 9am tomorrow. I'll have lumber delivered and we'll set up scaffold and build temporary support walls.
